'''Gerald Home''' ([[October 18]], [[1950s#1950|1950]]-[[October 6]], [[2021]])<ref name="Jedi News obituary" /> was the mime artist/actor of [[Tessek/Legends|Tessek]] the [[Quarren/Legends|Quarren]] and the [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] [[Officer/Legends|officer]] [[Verrack/Legends|Verrack]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].

Since [[January]] [[2008]], he had acted as the official ambassador of S.W.O.R.A., the Star Wars Outer Rim Alliance. Home passed away due to liver cancer on [[October 6]], [[2021]].

